://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/ba24fff0-16b6-11ee-beef-6f2e631dd76c" style="height:2000px;width:3300px;" alt="Cowboy Cruiser 电动自行车车把的前视图。电话安装在中央。" data-uuid="71bbfb9c-cac8-3f29-9fb2-6bed6719c9e2"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">牛仔</div></figure><p>随着产品阵容越来越拥挤，Cowboy 重新命名了现有的电动自行车，“让客户更容易找到最适合他们个人需求的电动自行车。”最初的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/cowboy-4-electric-bike-launches-with-a-step-through-model-121513629.html">C4 型号</a>现在称为 Cowboy Classic，C4ST 更名为 Cruiser ST。</p><p> Cowboy Cruiser 从今天开始上市，“促销价”为 2,690 英镑（3,393.43 美元）。您可以从<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://us.cowboy.com/">公司网站</a>购买黑色和沙色的颜色。如果您想亲自浏览，该公司计划最终向欧洲 300 家自行车零售商推出电动自行车。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/cowboy-cruiser-e-bike-offers-a-more-upright-ride-000010102.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/cowboy-cruiser-e-bike-offers-a-more-upright-ride-000010102.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> be6eedb4-8983-43be-b12a-f3dabf7f0961</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jul 2023 00:00:10 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688384028</ingested><modified> 2023-07-03T11:33:51+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Automotive Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="1700" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/47d4a040-16b6-11ee-9ff7-f5d39cb38b44" width="3069"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:descripti